      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Modern Irrigation & Land Co.,\nare laying out a large tract of land\nin ten acre tracts six miles east of\nHoward street, in the garden spot of\nthe Spokane valley which they pro-\npose to irrigate from wells. operated\nby electricity. This tract is the\ncream of the Spokane valley. The\ncompany is DESTROYS of an appro-\npirate name and will pay $40 for the\nname they adopt. Competition open\nto all All names must be in by jan\nuary 20. Address Modern Irrigation\n& Land Co, Wolverton Block, Spo-\nkane, Wash."
